  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "Sau \u0111\xF3 \xCA-li-a-kim, S\u1EBFp-na, v\xE0 Gi\xF4-a x\xE9 qu\u1EA7n \xE1o m\xECnh \u0111\u1EC3 b\xE0y t\u1ECF l\xF2ng \u0111au bu\u1ED3n. \xCA-li-a-kim, con trai Hinh-kia, l\xE0 qu\u1EA3n l\xFD cung vua, S\u1EBFp-na l\xE0m \u0111\u1ED5ng l\xFD v\u0103n ph\xF2ng, c\xF2n Gi\xF4-a, con A-s\xE1p, l\xE0m k\xFD l\u1EE5c. Ba ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i g\u1EB7p vua \xCA-x\xEA-chia v\xE0 thu\u1EADt l\u1EA1i nh\u1EEFng g\xEC vi\xEAn t\u01B0 l\u1EC7nh t\xE1c chi\u1EBFn n\xF3i."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
